t"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score the Lead\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each email 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Assign Round-Robin Owner","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"b3f20257-263b-ee65-f68b-e314cebf11ac","name":"Note: Score the Lead"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Assign Round-Robin Owner\n\nCustom JavaScript: Round-robin owner assignment\n\nNext: Route by Heat","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"f0daeeb4-ba09-0ce1-0306-7ee5c7d07888","name":"Note: Assign Round-Robin Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Heat\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: hot, warm + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping · ②→ Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams · ③→ Cold → Park in Nurture List","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"6abdbc92-3fe2-e68d-4a0b-5339cd90f85d","name":"Note: Route by Heat"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Notify Assigned Owner · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,40],"id":"86d3be2a-63c2-3d6d-e070-0dc9aa7fd378","name":"Note: Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Notify Assigned Owner\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,40],"id":"c3431a66-5f5b-99b2-c52c-5d4e7bbc452e","name":"Note: Notify Assigned Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"3b837c2d-e27f-2584-2735-38232938faf3","name":"Note: Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cold → Park in Nurture List\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1000],"id":"9a1f9379-54a3-ed7a-6a62-c72357bb8348","name":"Note: Cold → Park in Nurture List"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Combine Lead Paths\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"82210323-1469-252f-d7d3-b2412244f89a","name":"Note: Combine Lead Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"9d7cad98-d1e4-207d-8e5a-c9010806f93e","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"694ab4f5-4820-a829-f0ef-79b465d51b4a","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"11e55093-50b8-3d79-0996-ea268b73c749","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"aa4aa9c6-8a67-c8da-6741-38105e014db7","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"2995e9ac-8222-9c75-86cc-2935e701308d","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"1cc03052-4fc4-971b-5e72-ea78b2d319bc","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Onboard subscribers with Google Sheets and Microsoft Teams with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** Drip Sequence · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nOnboard subscribers with Google Sheets and Microsoft Teams with instant alerts. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual auto-responders is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Stamp & Shape Email → Payload Valid? → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to drip sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating auto-responders in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"68deb471-1b97-9bc7-58f6-9e6030c79e7e","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"c0a4bacd-35b2-de0e-5c66-313ecfc3e43b","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your auto-responders process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"63fb7312-e1e7-9baf-8585-662ba17cdf3b","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Score the Lead","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score the Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Assign Round-Robin Owner","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Assign Round-Robin Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Heat","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping":{"main":[[{"node":"Notify Assigned Owner","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Heat":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Cold → Park in Nurture List","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Notify Assigned Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warm → Drip via Microsoft Teams":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cold → Park in Nurture List":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Combine Lead Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"7d87e418-555e-468f-a1c0-e96eabd1c799","id":"FDX02727"}